response.original_title: 20th Century Masters - The Best of Asia
response.overview: Rock supergroup Asia were originally cast from member of Yes, Emerson, Lake and Palmer, and other UK rock gods. Often performing intricate, progressive rock-influenced tunes, the band gained a loyal following for their own unique contribution to the genre. This collection brings together a selection of their music videos, including "The Smile Has Left Your Eyes," "Only Time Will Tell," and more.
response.title: 20th Century Masters - The Best of Asia
